	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am also a big beliver in putting your points into stamina.&nbsp;&nbsp;When you start out with zero money 300pp for a Fighting baton and 40-60pp for each piece of Wu's can be hard to obtain.  I recommend you start by trying to get some raw silk first, progress to cured silk, and then go to Wu's/ other armor items.  As far as a weapon goes a good cheap 1 HB is the snarak enforcer which goes for about 50pp.  Have fun!  <br><br>Uniero<br>42 Monk<br>Officer Odin's Ghost<br>7th Hammer<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
